    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{cases} h(0) = 520 \\\\ h(5) = 530 \\\\ h(15) = 520 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} C = 520 \\\\ \\frac{125}{3}a + \\frac{25}{2}b + C = 530 \\\\ \\frac{15^3}{3}a + \\frac{15^2}{2}b + C = 520 \\end{cases} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} a = -\\frac{3}{25} \\\\ b = \\frac{6}{5} \\\\ C = 520 \\end{cases} \\Rightarrow h(t) = -\\frac{3}{25}t^3 + \\frac{6}{5}t^2 + 520\n$$"
